{{WikiProject Languages}} 

Hey folks,

I just wanted to pass this along although it's old news.  I was reading the book "Λεξικολογία" (Lexicology) by Γιώργος Ξυδόπουλος (Giorgos Xydopoulos) from 2008 in which he surveys everything from current electronic dictionaries to active and passive vocabulary, quite a wide range of things... Anyways in the chapter on morphology he has a chart comparing phonemes and writing for both English and Greek, and he credits en wikibooks [[English/Spelling]] for the data on English :-) Happy trails! -- [[User:ArielGlenn|ArielGlenn]] ([[User talk:ArielGlenn|talk]]) 04:17, 13 April 2010 (UTC)

