where: * ''page'' is the Wikispecies article to link to. Defaults to '''PAGENAME''' (the current page's title) * ''link text'' is the text to display with the above link. Defaults to ''page''. <includeonly> <!-- ADD CATEGORIES BELOW THIS LINE --> [[Category:Interwiki link templates|{{PAGENAME}}]] </includeonly>

